Ext.data.JsonP['Hyperloop_3.0.0_Release_Note']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Hyperloop 3.0.0 - 17 November 2017</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-52298138\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Hyperloop 3.0.0 - 17 November 2017</h1>\n    <p>Hyperloop 3.0.0 is a major release that includes new features, improvements, and bug fixes.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-52298138_Hyperloop3.0.0ReleaseNote-Newfeatures\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>New features</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-24657\" target=\"_blank\">TIMOB-24657</a> - Hyperloop: Android - Support to catch native exceptions    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Added feature that catches native exceptions    </p>\n</li></ul></li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-52298138_Hyperloop3.0.0ReleaseNote-Improvements\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Improvements</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-25340\" target=\"_blank\">TIMOB-25340</a> - Hyperloop: Move to using auto-required &apos;hooks&apos; folder, not plugin    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>As part of the integration of Hyperloop into SDK core, the <tt class=\" \">&lt;plugins&gt;</tt> tag is no longer needed for Hyperloop    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-25399\" target=\"_blank\">TIMOB-25399</a> - Windows: Hyperloop to drop Windows 8.1 support    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Removed support for Windows 8.1    </p>\n</li></ul></li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-52298138_Hyperloop3.0.0ReleaseNote-Fixedissues\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Fixed issues</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-25079\" target=\"_blank\">TIMOB-25079</a> - Use JavaScriptCore by default    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=52298138\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Hyperloop 3.0.0 Release Note"});